---
import { AppConfig } from "../../data";
---

<section class="Slide">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="content">
            <p>Two core customer types. Both ambitious. Both underserved by generic tech providers.</p>
            <div class="audience-wrapper">
                <div class="audience-card">
                    <div class="image">
                        <img src={ AppConfig.images.business_owner.src } alt="James the Business Owner">
                    </div>

                    <div class="content">
                        <p class="title">James - The Established Owner</p>
                        <p class="description">SME Owner · 30–50 · Nairobi</p>
                        <p class="subtitle">Goal</p>
                        <p>Scale the business without hiring an in-house tech team.</p>
                        <p class="subtitle">Pain points</p>
                        <p>Wasted money on agencies that delivered websites but no results. Frustrated by jargon and slow turnarounds.</p>
                        <p class="subtitle">Buys { AppConfig.brand_name } for</p>
                        <p>A reliable partner who handles digital from strategy to execution.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="audience-card">
                    <div class="image">
                        <img src={ AppConfig.images.woman_founder.src } alt="James the Business Owner">
                    </div>

                    <div class="content">
                        <p class="title">Amara — The Growth-Hungry Founder</p>
                        <p class="description">Startup Founder · 25–38 · East Africa</p>
                        <p class="subtitle">Goal</p>
                        <p>Build a digital presence that attracts investors and customers fast.</p>
                        <p class="subtitle">Pain points</p>
                        <p>Can't afford full-time developers. Has tried Fiverr freelancers with mixed results. Needs quality at speed.</p>
                        <p class="subtitle">Buys { AppConfig.brand_name } for</p>
                        <p>End-to-end branding and systems that position her startup to compete at a global level.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="content-title">SHARED INSIGHT</p>
            <p>Both audiences have been let down before. They're not buying a service — they're buying the trust that this time, it'll actually work.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
